<script type="text/javascript"> 
tlz._page = {
	productType: 'particulier',
  	product : 'nvei',
    parcoursType : 'form'
};
tlz._page.name = ({
    'form' : 'formulaire - vehicule',
    'tarif' : 'complete - avec tarif'
})[tc_vars.page_name];
tlz._page.context = (tlz.isIframe() && tlz.parseUrl(tlz.referrer).host == 'www.allianz.fr') ? 'allianz' : 'standalone';
//event category
tlz._eventCategory = 'formulaire - espace prospect - par - nvei - demande devis';
// conversionType
tlz.evt.on('step', function(e){
  tlz._page.conversionType = tlz.contains(e.detail,'avec tarif') && 'confirmation';
});
</script>

tag_name: Obj - session | Macros - session - session id
script:
<script type="text/javascript"> 
tlz._session = tlz.store.getObj('session');
if (tlz._page.context == 'allianz'){
  tlz.msg.send({ 'message': 'request var', 'requested_var': 'tlz._session.sessionId', 'url': tlz.url });
  tlz.x1('listen msg var', function(){
    tlz.msg.on(function(data){
      if (data.message == 'send var ' + 'tlz._session.sessionId'){
        tlz.setMacro('sessionId', { session: 'session', value: data.value });
      }
    }, { origins: /\.allianz\.fr/ });
  });
} else {
  tlz.setMacro('sessionId', {
    session: 'session',
    rule: function(m){
      return !m._val
    },
    value: tlz.guid().replace(/-/g, '')
  });
}
</script>

<script type="text/javascript"> 
tlz._nvei = tlz.store.getObj('nvei');
if (tc_vars.page_name == 'form') {
  tlz.store.clearObj('nvei');
}
//macros
if (tc_vars.conversion_file_id) {
  tlz._nvei.idDevis = tc_vars.conversion_file_id;
}
tlz.doWhen(function() { return tlz.$1('.vehicule-option--active') }, function() {
  tlz.setMacro('type', { local: 'nvei', norm: true, value: tlz.$1('.vehicule-option--active').getAttribute('for'), noHeritage: true });
})
if (tlz._page.context == 'allianz') {
  tlz.msg.send({ 'message': 'request var', 'requested_var': 'tlz._alz.birthYear', 'url': tlz.url });
  tlz.x1('listen msg var' + ' tlz._alz.birthYear', function() {
    tlz.msg.on(function(data) {
      if (data.message == 'send var ' + 'tlz._alz.birthYear' && data.value) {
        tlz.setMacro('birthYear', { local: 'nvei', value: data.value });
      }
    }, { origins: /\.allianz\.fr/ });
  });
}
tlz.L2(document.body).on(['mouseup', 'change'], '.form :input, form .select, .content-left form select', function(e) {
  setTimeout(function() {
    if (tlz.$1('input[name=zipCode]')) {
      tlz.setMacro('zipCode', { local: 'nvei', norm: true, value: tlz.$1('input[name=zipCode]').value, noHeritage: true });
    }
    if (tlz.$1('input[name=city]')) {
      tlz.setMacro('city', { local: 'nvei', norm: true, value: tlz.$1('input[name=city]').value, noHeritage: true });
    }
    if (tlz.$1('input[name=mail]')) {
      tlz.setMacro('email', { noHeritage: true, user: 'alz', local: 'nvei', type: 'email', value: tlz.$1('input[name=mail]').value });
      //set email to parent page
      tlz.msg.send({
        'message': 'fnOv',
        'fnStr': encodeURI((function() {
          tlz.setMacro('email', { user: 'alz', type: 'email', value: tlz._msgFnParam });
        }).toString()),
        'fnParam': tlz._nvei.email
      });
    }
    if (tlz.$1('.vehicule-option--active')) {
      tlz.setMacro('type', { local: 'nvei', norm: true, value: tlz.$1('.vehicule-option--active').getAttribute('for'), noHeritage: true });
    }
  }, 250);
}, true);
tlz.dR(function() {
  if (tc_vars.page_name && tc_vars.page_name == 'tarif') {
    tlz._tarifs = tlz.txt(tlz.$1('tfoot')).split(/â‚¬\D+/);
    tlz.doForEach(tlz._tarifs, function(v) {
      tlz._tarif = tlz.toNum(v);
      tlz.setMacro('tarifMin', { local: 'nvei', rule: function(m) { return !m._val || m.val < m._val }, value: tlz._tarif });
    });
  }
}, true);
if (tlz._page.context == 'allianz') {
  tlz.msg.send({ 'message': 'request setContext' });
  tlz.x1('listen msg request nvei', function() {
    tlz.msg.on(function(data) {
      if (data.message == 'send setContext') {
        tlz.setMacro('actionCo', { local: 'nvei', value: data.value.actionCo, noHeritage: true });
        tlz.setMacro('sourceAN', { local: 'nvei', value: data.value.sourceAN, noHeritage: true });
        if (window.setContext) {
          setContext({ source: tlz._nvei.sourceAN, actionCo: tlz._nvei.actionCo });
        }
      }
    }, { origins: /\.allianz\.fr/ });
  });
}
</script>

<script type="text/javascript"> 
tlz.x1('init 1000m', function(){
    tlz.tro('session_ttl', 1800);
    tlz.tro('init', '6547792-6dc68d6d6631e0e7ce1307e7e05a8995'); //alz
});
tlz.x1('listen step 1000m',function(){
    tlz.evt.on('step', function(e){
        tlz._troParams = {
            rtgenv: tc_vars.env, //production, recette
            rtgdevice: tlz.device(), //desktop, tablet, mobile
            //rtglogged : tlz._alz.logged || 0, //1, 0
            rtguser_category: tlz._alz.userType || 'prospect', //prospect, client
            sha256: tlz._alz.customerEmail, // email du client
           	rtgcustomer_id: tlz._alz.dmpOptin ? tlz._alz.customerId : undefined,
            rtgpagename: tlz.title,
            rtgespace_id: tlz._page.productType, //particulier
            rtgunivers_id: tlz._page.productLine, //gamme produit
            rtgidcat: tlz._page.productCategory, //categorie niveau 2 du menu
            rtgidproduit: tlz._page.product, //nvei
            rtgparcours: tlz._page.parcoursType, //form
            rtgstep: (e.detail||'').replace(/ - /g,'-'), //etape tunnel
            rtgconversion_code: tc_vars.conversion_code, //code an
            rtgconversion: tlz._page.conversionType ? 1 : 0,
            rtgconversion_type: tlz._page.conversionType || undefined, //confirmation
            rtgconversion_file_id: tlz._nvei.idDevis, //id devis an
            rtgconversion_low_offer: tlz._nvei.tarifMin, // tarif annuel min
            rtgconversion_sha256: tlz._nvei.email,
            rtgconversion_yearofbirth: tlz._nvei.birthYear,
            rtgconversion_city: tlz._nvei.city,
            rtgconversion_postal_code: tlz._nvei.zipCode
        };
        if (tlz._page.context == 'affiliation'){
          tlz._troParams.rtgparcours = 'form_pdl';
        }
        tlz.tro('tag', tlz._troParams);
    });
});
</script>

tag_name: UA - optout, init, dims, path, page, onga
script:
<script type='text/javascript'>
//optout
tlz._disableGA = function(){
	window['ga-disable-UA-33617477-8'] = !0;
	tlz._isGADisabled = !0;
  	tlz.warn('GA is disabled');
};
if(tlz.cookie.get('disable-ga')){
	tlz._disableGA();
}
if (tlz._page.context != 'standalone'){
  //init
  tlz.x1('init - create ua tracker', function(){
        tlz.ua('create', 'UA-33617477-8', 'auto', { cookieExpires: 34214400, siteSpeedSampleRate: 10 });
        tlz.ua('require', 'displayfeatures');
        tlz.ua('set', 'anonymizeIp', true);
  });
  //session dims
  tlz.x1('ga_session_dim', function(){
      var fakeAd = document.createElement('div');
      fakeAd.id = 'topAd';
      fakeAd.setAttribute('style', 'height:1px; width:1px');
      if(document && document.body){
          document.body.appendChild(fakeAd);
      }
      tlz.ua('set', {
          dimension8: tlz.userAgent,
          dimension28: !tlz.$1('#topAd') && '(not set)' || tlz.$1('#topAd').offsetHeight === 0 && 'oui' || 'non',
          dimension102: tlz._session.sessionId
      });
  }, 'session');
  tlz.ua('set', {
    dimension7: tlz._nvei.idDevis
  });
  //path
  tlz.ua('set','page', '/formulaire-devis-nvei/'+tc_vars.page_name);
}
//pageview
tlz.setMacro('id1000Mercis', { user: 'alz', value: tlz.cookie.get('__troRUID') });
tlz.setMacro('id1000Mercis', { user: 'tmn', value: tlz.cookie.get('__troRUID') });
if (tlz._page.context == 'allianz'){
  if(tc_vars.page_name=='tarif'){
    var ua_args = ['send', 'pageview', { page: tlz.parseUrl(tlz.referrer).pathname + 'tarif' }];
    tlz.msg.send({'message': 'ga', 'value' : ua_args});
  }
}
else{
  if (tlz._alz.clientIdGA){
      tlz.ua('send', 'pageview', { dimension74: tlz._alz.clientIdGA, dimension75: tlz._alz.id1000Mercis });
  } else {
      tlz.ua(function(tracker){
          tlz.setMacro('clientIdGA', { user: 'alz', value: window.ga.getAll()[0].get('clientId') });
          tracker.send('pageview', { dimension74: tlz._alz.clientIdGA, dimension75: tlz._alz.id1000Mercis });
          if (tlz._alz.clientIdGA){
              tlz.x1('send ga', function(){
                  tlz.evt.send('ga');
              });
          }
      });
  }
}
//onga
tlz.x1('set onga',function(){
    tlz._onGa = function(cbk){
        if(tlz._alz.clientIdGA){
            cbk();
        } else {
            tlz.evt.on('ga', function(){
                cbk();
            });
        }
    };
});
</script>

<script type="text/javascript"> 
tlz.x1('1000m set id ga', function(){
    tlz._onGa(function(){
        tlz.tro('tag', { rtgidga: tlz._alz.clientIdGA });
    });
});
</script>

<script type='text/javascript'>
  tlz.msg.on(function(data){
    if (data.message == 'cm_lead_snapchat'){
      var fun_args = function(){
        (function(e, t, n){
          if (e.snaptr) return;
          var a = e.snaptr = function(){
            a.handleRequest ? a.handleRequest.apply(a, arguments) : a.queue.push(arguments)
          };
          a.queue = [];
          tlz.js(n);
        })(window, document,
           'https://sc-static.net/scevent.min.js');
        snaptr('init', 'aa200853-a45a-4209-b60e-a2898eb44ae7', {
          'user_email': tlz._msgFnParam
        });
        snaptr('track', 'SIGN_UP');
      };
      tlz.x1('lead snapchat ' + tlz._nvei.type, function(){
        if (tlz._page.context == 'allianz'){
          tlz.msg.send({ 'message': 'fnOv', 'fnStr': encodeURI(fun_args.toString()), 'fnParam': tlz._nvei.email || tlz._alz.customerEmail });
        } else {
          tlz.oV('tmn', 'cookies', function(){
            tlz._msgFnParam = tlz._nvei.email || tlz._alz.customerEmail;
            fun_args.apply();
          });
        }
      }, 'session');
    }
  }, {origins: /allianz.fr/});
</script>

<script type="text/javascript"> 
var fun_args = function(){
  (function(e, t, n){
    if (e.snaptr) return;
    var a = e.snaptr = function(){
      a.handleRequest ? a.handleRequest.apply(a, arguments) : a.queue.push(arguments)
    };
    a.queue = [];
    tlz.js(n);
  })(window, document,
    'https://sc-static.net/scevent.min.js');
  snaptr('init', 'aa200853-a45a-4209-b60e-a2898eb44ae7', {
    'user_email': tlz._msgFnParam
  });
  snaptr('track', 'VIEW_CONTENT');
};
if (tlz._page.context == 'allianz'){
  tlz.msg.send({ 'message': 'fnOv', 'fnStr': encodeURI(fun_args.toString()), 'fnParam': tlz._nvei.email || tlz._alz.customerEmail });
} else {
  tlz.oV('tmn', 'cookies', function(){
    fun_args.apply();

<script type='text/javascript'>
tlz.x1('ua event - download external links', function() {
    var isExternalDomain = new RegExp('((espaceclient\\.|e)allianz\\.fr)([\\/\\?#]|$)')
    var isInternalDomain = new RegExp('(' + tlz.topDomain.replace('.', '\\.') + '|mmtro\\.com)([\\/\\?#]|$)');
    var getExtension = function(txt) {
        return txt && txt.replace('pdf.html', '.pdf').match(/[\/\.](pdf|jpe?g|png|gif|(doc|ppt|xls)x?|csv|rss|zip)([\?#]|$)/i);
    };
    var trackLink = function(text, category, action, label) {
        tlz.gt('event', action, {
            event_label: label,
            event_category: category,
            linkTitle_20: text || undefined,
            transport_type: 'beacon'
        });
    };
    tlz.L2(document).on('click', 'a', function() {
        var href = this.href;
        if (href) {
          var extension = getExtension(href) || getExtension(this.title);
          if (extension) {
            trackLink(tlz.txt(this), 'download', extension[1].toLowerCase(), href);
          } else if (/^(https?:)?\/\//.test(href) && (isExternalDomain.test(href) || !isInternalDomain.test(href))) {
            trackLink(tlz.txt(this), 'external-link', href);
          }
        }
    });
});
</script>

<script type="text/javascript">
tlz.x1('privacy', function() {
    // privacy center
    tlz.dR(function() {
        tlz._modifyEl = function(sel, cbk) {
            var el = tlz.$1(sel);
            if (el) { cbk(el); }
        };
        tlz._modifyEl('a[href*=utilisation-des-cookies],a[href*=gestion-des-cookies],.footer-item span:contains(cookies)', function(el) {
            el.innerHTML = ' G\xe9rer les cookies';
            el.href = '#showPrivacyCenter';
            el.setAttribute('data-destination', '#showPrivacyCenter');
        });
        tlz._modifyEl('.nx-footer .footers-cursor:contains(cookies)', function(el) { el.innerHTML = ' G\xe9rer les cookies'; });
        tlz._modifyEl('.nx-footer .nx-footer__link:contains(cookies)', function(el) { el.setAttribute('data-destination', '#showPrivacyCenter'); });
        tlz.doForEach(tlz.$('a[href="#showPrivacyCenter"],*[data-destination="#showPrivacyCenter"]'), function(link) {
            if (link.addEventListener) {
                link.addEventListener('click', function(e) { e.preventDefault();
                    e.stopPropagation();
                    window.OneTrust.ToggleInfoDisplay(); return !1; }, true);
            } else if (link.attachEvent) {
                link.attachEvent('onclick', function(e) { e.preventDefault();
                    e.stopPropagation();
                    window.OneTrust.ToggleInfoDisplay(); return !1; });
            }
        });
    });
    // set optin
    tlz._prevOptinCategories = tlz.getOptinCategories().split(',');
    tlz._saveOptin = function() {
        tlz._optinCategories = tlz.getOptinCategories();
        tlz.log('optinCategories:', tlz._optinCategories);

        });*/
        tlz.evt.send('saveOptin');
        tlz.doForEach(tlz._optinCategories.split(','), function(optinType) {
            if (!tlz.contains(tlz._prevOptinCategories, optinType)) {
                tlz.evt.send(optinType + 'Optin');

    // cmp
    if (cmp) {

                    non_interaction: true,
                    send_to: tlz._getConsentGaIds()
                });*/

            }
            /*if (e.action == 'retour') {

script:
<script type="text/javascript"> 
tlz._page = {
	productType: 'particulier',
  	product : 'auto',
    parcoursType : 'pl',
    univers: 'vehicules',
    rawProduct: 'auto'
};
if(tc_vars.conversion_funnel_nom_form.toLowerCase()=='souscription_auto'){
	tlz._page.parcoursType='souscription';
}
var angularPathNames = {
    '/commencer' : 'formulaire - commencer',
    '/commencer/' : 'formulaire - commencer',
    '/informations-conducteur' : 'formulaire - conducteur',
    '/informations-contact' : 'formulaire - coordonnees',
    '/devis/proposition-sans-tarif' : 'complete - proposition sans tarif',
    '/devis/exclusion' : 'complete - exclusion',
    '/options' : 'options',
    '/identification/e-mail' : 'mer email - formulaire',
    '/identification/rencontrer-agent' : 'mer agent - formulaire',
  	'/agences/rencontrer-agent': 'mer agent - liste agences',
    '/identification/etre-contacte' : 'mer tel - formulaire',
    '/souscription/resume' : 'recapitulatif, mandat',
    '/souscription/confirmation' : 'souscription'
};
tlz._page.name = angularPathNames[tlz.angularPath];
if(tlz.contains(tlz.angularPath,'/devis/tarification/questions')){
    tlz._page.name = 'complete - avec tarif';
} else if(tlz.contains(tlz.angularPath,'/devis/options/questions')){
    tlz._page.name = 'options';
} else if(tlz.contains(tlz.angularPath,'/devis/vehicule/questions')){
    tlz._page.name = 'formulaire - vehicule';
} else if(tlz.contains(tlz.angularPath,'/devis/driver/questions')){
    tlz._page.name = 'formulaire - conducteur';
} else if(tlz.contains(tlz.angularPath,'/devis/contact/questions')){
    tlz._page.name = 'formulaire - coordonnees';
} else if(/\/souscription\/(informations-personnelles|assurance)\//.test(tlz.angularPath)){
    tlz._page.name = 'formulaire - km, iban, assurance';
} else if(/\/souscription\/(resume|cotisation|signature)\//.test(tlz.angularPath)){
    tlz._page.name = 'recapitulatif, mandat';
}
//eventcategory
tlz._eventCategory = tlz._page.parcoursType=='souscription' ? 'auto - souscription' : 'auto - devis - pl';
// conversionType merType
tlz.evt.on('step', function(e){
  tlz._page.merType = tlz.contains(e.detail,'mer') && 'mer_'+ e.detail.split(' -')[0].replace('mer ','');
  tlz._page.conversionType = tlz.contains(e.detail,'avec tarif') ? 'ta_'+tlz._page.parcoursType :
  tlz.contains(e.detail,'proposition') ? 'pst_'+tlz._page.parcoursType :
  tlz.contains(e.detail,'confirmation') ? tlz._page.merType :
  e.detail == 'souscription' ? e.detail :
  null;
});
//is same domain
tlz._cookieSameSite = false;
if (tlz.isIframe()) {
  var parentTopDomain = tlz.referrer.split('//')[1].split('/')[0].split('.');
  parentTopDomain = parentTopDomain[parentTopDomain.length - 2];
  if (parentTopDomain != tlz.topDomain.split('.')[0]) {
  	tlz._cookieSameSite = true; 
  }
}
</script>

<script type="text/javascript"> 
tlz._setOptinCategories = function(){
    var optinTypeIds = {
        'analytics': ['4', '10', '20', '27', '31'],
        'cookies': ['5', '11', '22', '29', '33']
    };
    var optinCategories = [];
    var tcOptinCookie = tlz.cookie.get('TC_OPTOUT_rgpd_categories');
    if (tcOptinCookie){
        tcOptinCategories = tcOptinCookie.split('%2C');
        tlz.doForEach(optinTypeIds, function(optinIds, optinType){
            var optinTypeStatus = !1;
            tlz.doForEach(tcOptinCategories, function(optinId){
                if (tlz.contains(optinIds, optinId)){
                    optinTypeStatus = !0;
                }
            });
            if (optinTypeStatus){
                optinCategories.push(optinType);
            }
            tlz.setMacro(optinType + 'Optin', { value: optinTypeStatus, user: 'alz' });
            tlz['_' + optinType + 'Optin'] = optinTypeStatus;
        });
    }
    tlz._optinCategories = optinCategories.join(',') || 'none'
};
tlz._setOptinCategories();
</script>

script:
<script type="text/javascript"> 
  tlz._auto = tlz.store.getObj('auto') || {};
if(window.angular && tlz.angularPath == '/commencer'){
  window.angular.element('[ng-app]').injector().invoke(['$context', '$parse', function($context, $parse){
    if(!$parse('vehicleDetails.myVehicle.type')($context.getState())){
      tlz.store.clearObj('auto');
    }
  }]);
}
//macros
tlz._auto.idDevis = tc_vars.conversion_file_id || tlz._auto.idDevis;
tlz._refreshScope = function(scope) {
  for(var key in scope) {
    if(tlz.is(scope[key])) {
      if(tlz.contains(['tarif', 'tarifMin'], key)) {
        scope[key] = tlz.toNum(scope[key]);
      } else if(tlz.contains(['email', 'gender', 'city', 'promo', 'formule', 'formuleRecommandee', 'formuleRecommandation', 'parkingCity', 'immatriculation', 'typeMine', 'model', 'brand', 'energy', 'insuranceDuration', 'searchSource', 'periodicity'], key)) {
        scope[key] = tlz.norm(scope[key]).replace(/<\/?[a-z]\>/g,'');
      } else if(tlz.contains(['birthDate', 'immatriculationDate', 'previousInsuranceTerm'], key)) {
        scope[key] = tlz.formatDate(scope[key]);
      } else if(tlz.contains(['zipCode', 'optinEmailSMS', 'parkingZipCode', 'bonus', 'assistedCar', 'assistedCarValid', 'assistedCarFlag', 'isHamon', 'fileDetails'], key)) {
        scope[key] = scope[key];
      }
      if(tlz.contains(['tarif', 'tarifMin', 'formuleRecommandation', 'immatriculationDate', 'parkingZipCode', 'parkingCity', 'immatriculation', 'typeMine', 'model', 'brand', 'energy', 'fileDetails'], key)) {
        tlz._auto[key] = scope[key];
      }
      tlz._updateObj = !0;
    }
  }
  
  tlz.setMacro('gender', { noHeritage:true, user:'alz', local:'auto', value:tlz.is(scope.gender) ? /wo|f/i.test(scope.gender) ? 'f' : 'h' : undefined });
  tlz.setMacro('zipCode', { noHeritage:true, user:'alz', local:'auto', norm:true, value: scope.zipCode });
  tlz.setMacro('city', { noHeritage:true, user:'alz', local:'auto', norm:true, value: scope.city });
  tlz.setMacro('birthYear', { noHeritage:true, user:'alz', local:'auto', type:'year', value:scope.birthDate });
  tlz.setMacro('email', { noHeritage:true, user:'alz', local:'auto', type:'email', value: scope.email });
  tlz.setMacro('immatriculationYear', { local:'auto', type:'year', value:scope.immatriculationDate });
  if(tlz.is(scope.optinEmailSMS)) {
    scope.optinEmailSMS = scope.optinEmailSMS == 'true' ? 'oui' : 'non';
    if(scope.optinEmailSMS != tlz._auto.optinEmailSMS) {
      tlz._auto.optinEmailSMS = scope.optinEmailSMS;
    }
  }
  if(tlz.is(scope.insuranceDuration) && tlz.is(scope.previousInsuranceTerm) && tlz.is(scope.isHamon)) {
    if(scope.insuranceDuration == 'un_an_et_plus') {
      tlz._auto.isHamon = scope.isHamon ? 'oui' : 'non';
    } else {
      tlz._auto.isHamon = 'ineligible';
    }
  }
  if(tlz.is(scope.formuleRecommandee)) {
    scope.formuleRecommandee = scope.formuleRecommandee.replace('au ', '');
    if(scope.formuleRecommandee != tlz._auto.formuleRecommandee) {
      tlz._auto.formuleRecommandee = scope.formuleRecommandee;
      tlz.gt('set', {
        formuleRecommandee_43: tlz._auto.formuleRecommandee
      });
    }
  }
  if(tlz.is(scope.formule)) {
    scope.formule = scope.formule.replace('au ', '');
    if(scope.formule != tlz._auto.formule) {
      tlz._auto.formule = scope.formule;
      tlz.gt('set', {
        formule_39: tlz._auto.formule
      });
    }
  }
  if(tlz.is(tlz._auto.formule) && tlz.is(tlz._auto.formuleRecommandee)) {
    scope.isRecommandee = tlz._auto.formule == tlz._auto.formuleRecommandee ? 'oui' : 'non';
    if(scope.isRecommandee != tlz._auto.isRecommandee) {
      tlz._auto.isRecommandee = scope.isRecommandee;
      tlz.gt('set', {
        isRecommandee_38: tlz._auto.isRecommandee
      });
    }
  }
  
  if(tlz.is(scope.promo) && scope.promo != tlz._auto.promo) {
    tlz._auto.promo = scope.promo;
    tlz.gt('set', {
        promo_40: tlz._auto.promo
      });
  }
  if(tlz.is(scope.bonus)) {
    if(scope.bonus > 4) {
      scope.bonus /= 100;
    }
    tlz._auto.bonus = tlz.toFloat(scope.bonus);
    tlz._auto.bonusBucket = '' + (Math.round(tlz._auto.bonus * 10) / 10);
  }
  if(tlz.is(scope.searchSource)) {
    scope.searchSource = scope.searchSource == 'siv' ? 'plaque' : 'criteres';
    if(scope.searchSource !== tlz._auto.modeRecherche) {
      tlz._auto.modeRecherche = scope.searchSource;
      tlz.gt('event', 'mode recherche vehicule', {
        event_label: tlz._auto.modeRecherche,
        event_category: tlz._eventCategory
      });
    }
  }
  if(scope.assistedCarFlag !== tlz._auto.canBeAssisted) {
    tlz._auto.canBeAssisted = scope.assistedCarFlag;
    if(tlz._auto.canBeAssisted) {
      tlz.gt('event', 'vehicule assiste', {
        event_label: 'affichage',
        event_category: tlz._eventCategory
      });
      
    }
  }
  if(tlz._auto.canBeAssisted) {
    if(scope.assistedCar !== tlz._auto.isAssisted) {
      tlz._auto.isAssisted = scope.assistedCar;
      tlz.gt('event', 'vehicule assiste', {
        event_label: 'choix - ' + (tlz._auto.isAssisted ? 'oui' : 'non'),
        event_category: tlz._eventCategory
      });
    }
    if(scope.assistedCarValid !== tlz._auto.isTrulyAssisted) {
      tlz._auto.isTrulyAssisted = scope.assistedCarValid;
      tlz.gt('event', 'vehicule assiste', {
        event_label: 'confirmation popin - ' + (tlz._auto.isTrulyAssisted ? 'oui' : 'non'),
        event_category: tlz._eventCategory
      });
    }
  }
  if(scope.periodicity){
    tlz._auto.periodicity = scope.periodicity == 'monthly' ? 'mensuel' : 'annuel';
  }
  if(tlz._updateObj) {
    tlz.store.setObj('auto');
    tlz._updateObj = !1;
  }
};
(function() {
  if(window.angular) {
    var $injector = window.angular.element('[ng-app]').injector();
    var TOKENS = {
      'email': 'contactDetails.email',
      'gender': 'contactDetails.gender',
      'birthDate': 'driverDetails.birthDate',
      'zipCode': 'contactDetails.city.postCode',
      'city': 'contactDetails.city.cityName',
      'previousInsuranceTerm': 'vehicleDetails.vehicleInsurance.previousInsuranceTerm',
      'insuranceDuration': 'vehicleDetails.vehicleInsurance.insuranceDuration',
      'isHamon': 'vehicleDetails.vehicleInsurance.acceptHamonTermination',
      'optinEmailSMS': 'contactDetails.receiveOffers',
      'tarif': 'tariffResult.proposal.offerAdvised.annualPayment',
      'tarifMin': 'tariffResult.proposal.offers[0].annualPayment',
      'promo': 'quotationDetails.actualPromo && (quotationDetails.actualPromo.shortText || "(not set)")',
      'formule': 'quotationDetails.name',

    var throttle;
    $injector.invoke(['$context', '$rootScope', '$parse', function($context, $rootScope, $parse) {
      function mapper(state) {
        var stateMapped = {};
        window.angular.forEach(TOKENS, function(expression, key) {
          var value = $parse(expression)(state);
          if(tlz.is(value)) {
            stateMapped[key] = value;
          }
        });
        return stateMapped;
      }
      tlz.x1('watch rootscope', function() {
        $rootScope.$watch(
          function() {
            return JSON.stringify(mapper($context.getState()));
          },
          function(newValue) {
            clearTimeout(throttle);
            throttle = setTimeout(function() {
              tlz._refreshScope(JSON.parse(newValue));
            }, 100);
          }
        );
      });
      tlz._refreshScope(tlz.clone(mapper($context.getState())));
    }]);
  }
}());

script:
<script type="text/javascript">
tlz.x1('privacy', function() {
    tlz._optinBanner = 'rgpd-footer-v2';
    window.tc_privacy_cookie_name = 'TC_OPTOUT_rgpd';
    tlz.L2(document).on('click', '#footer_tc_privacy_button_2', function() {
        tlz.$1('#footer_tc_privacy_button').click();
    });

    tlz._saveOptin = function(button) {
        tlz._prevOptinCategories = tlz._optinCategories.replace('ads', 'cookies').split(',');
        tlz._setOptinCategories();
        tlz.doForEach(tlz._optinCategories.replace('ads', 'cookies').split(','), function(optinType) {
            if (!tlz.contains(tlz._prevOptinCategories, optinType)) {
                  tlz.evt.send(optinType + 'Optin');
                tlz.gt('set', {
                    optinCategories_103: tlz._optinCategories,
                    optinAds_136: (tlz._alz.cookiesOptin || tlz._alz.adsOptin || tlz._cookiesOptin || tlz._adsOptin) ? '1' : '0',
                    optinAnalytics_137: tlz._alz.analyticsOptin ? '1' : '0',
                    optinPerso_138: (tlz._alz.cookiesOptin || tlz._alz.adsOptin || tlz._cookiesOptin || tlz._adsOptin) ? '1' : '0'
                });
                tlz.gt('event', 'optin', {
                    event_category: 'privacy - ' + tlz._optinBanner,
                    event_label: optinType,
                    privacyId_134: '' + tC.privacyID,
                    privacyVersion_135: tC.privacyVersion,
                    non_interaction: true
                });
            }
        });
        tlz.gt('event', 'close banner', {
            event_category: 'privacy - ' + tlz._optinBanner,
            event_label: button,
            privacyId_134: '' + tC.privacyID,
            privacyVersion_135: tC.privacyVersion,
            non_interaction: true
        });
    };

    window.tc_showPrivacy = function() {
        tlz.gt('event', 'show banner', {
            event_category: 'privacy - ' + tlz._optinBanner,
            privacyId_134: ''+tC.privacyID,
            privacyVersion_135: tC.privacyVersion,
            non_interaction: true
        });
    };
    window.tc_showPrivacyCenter = function() {
        tlz.gt('event', 'show privacy center', {
            event_category: 'privacy - ' + tlz._optinBanner,
            privacyId_134: ''+tC.privacyID,
            privacyVersion_135: tC.privacyVersion,
            non_interaction: true
        });
    };
    window.tc_closePrivacyButton = function() {
        tlz._saveOptin('accepter tout');
    };
    window.tc_closePrivacyCenter = function(t) {
        if (t == 'save') {
            tlz._saveOptin('privacy center');
        } else {
            tlz.gt('event', 'close privacy center', {
                event_category: 'privacy - ' + tlz._optinBanner,
                privacyId_134: ''+tC.privacyID,
                privacyVersion_135: tC.privacyVersion,
                non_interaction: true
            });
        }
    };
});
</script>

script:
<script type="text/javascript"> 
tlz._page = {
	productType: 'particulier',
  	product : 'auto',
    parcoursType : 'pl',
    univers: 'vehicules',
    rawProduct: 'auto'
};
if(tc_vars.conversion_funnel_nom_form.toLowerCase()=='souscription_auto'){
	tlz._page.parcoursType='souscription';
}
tlz._page.name = ({
    '/accueil' : 'formulaire - vehicule',
    '/informations-conducteur' : 'formulaire - conducteur',
    '/informations-contact' : 'formulaire - coordonnees',
    '/tarification' : 'complete - avec tarif',
    '/proposition-sans-tarif' : 'complete - proposition sans tarif',
    '/exclusion' : 'complete - exclusion',
    '/options' : 'options',
    '/identification/email' : 'mer email - formulaire',
    '/identification/rencontrer-agent' : 'mer agent - formulaire',
    '/agences/rencontrer-agent' : 'mer agent - liste agences',
    '/souscription/informations' : 'formulaire - km, iban, assurance',
    '/souscription/recapitulatif' : 'recapitulatif, mandat',
    '/souscription/confirmation' : 'souscription'
})[tlz.angularPath];
// eventcategory
tlz._eventCategory = tlz._page.parcoursType=='souscription' ? 'auto - souscription' : 'auto - devis - pl';
// conversionType && merType
tlz.evt.on('step', function(e){
  tlz._page.merType = tlz.contains(e.detail,'mer') && 'mer_'+ e.detail.split(' -')[0].replace('mer ','');
  tlz._page.conversionType = tlz.contains(e.detail,'avec tarif') ? 'ta_'+tlz._page.parcoursType :
  tlz.contains(e.detail,'proposition') ? 'pst_'+tlz._page.parcoursType :
  tlz.contains(e.detail,'confirmation') ? tlz._page.merType :
  e.detail == 'souscription' ? e.detail :
  null;
});
//is same domain
tlz._cookieSameSite = false;
if (tlz.isIframe()) {
  var parentTopDomain = tlz.referrer.split('//')[1].split('/')[0].split('.');
  parentTopDomain = parentTopDomain[parentTopDomain.length - 2];
  if (parentTopDomain != tlz.topDomain.split('.')[0]) {
  	tlz._cookieSameSite = true; 
  }
}
</script>

<script type="text/javascript"> 
tlz._setOptinCategories = function(){
    var optinTypeIds = {
        'analytics': ['4', '10', '20', '27', '31'],
        'cookies': ['5', '11', '22', '29', '33']
    };
    var optinCategories = [];
    var tcOptinCookie = tlz.cookie.get('TC_OPTOUT_rgpd_categories');
    if (tcOptinCookie){
        tcOptinCategories = tcOptinCookie.split('%2C');
        tlz.doForEach(optinTypeIds, function(optinIds, optinType){
            var optinTypeStatus = !1;
            tlz.doForEach(tcOptinCategories, function(optinId){
                if (tlz.contains(optinIds, optinId)){
                    optinTypeStatus = !0;
                }
            });
            if (optinTypeStatus){
                optinCategories.push(optinType);
            }
            tlz.setMacro(optinType + 'Optin', { value: optinTypeStatus, user: 'alz' });
            tlz['_' + optinType + 'Optin'] = optinTypeStatus;
        });
    }
    tlz._optinCategories = optinCategories.join(',') || 'none'
};
tlz._setOptinCategories();
</script>

tlz._doesWatcherExist = function(watcherExp, watcherCbk) {
  var doesWatcherExist = false;
  if (tlz._scope) {
    tlz.doForEach(tlz._scope.$$watchers, function(watcher) {
      if (watcher.exp === watcherExp && (watcherCbk && watcher.fn.name === watcherCbk || !watcherCbk)) {
        doesWatcherExist = true;
      }
    });
  }
  return doesWatcherExist;
};
tlz._watch = function(k, fn, deepWatch) {
  if (!tlz._doesWatcherExist(k, 'cbk')) {
    if (tlz._scope) {
      tlz._scope.$watch(k, function cbk(v) {
        fn(v, k);
      }, deepWatch);
    }
  }
};

if (window.angular) {
  tlz._scope = window.angular.element('[ng-view]').scope();
  if (tlz._scope) {
    if (tlz._scope.vehicleDetails) {
      tlz.setMacro('isNewVehicle', {local:'auto', transform:function(v){return v=='NEW' ? 1 : 0}, value:tlz.getProp('tlz._scope.vehicleDetails.myVehicle.type')});
      tlz._auto.immatriculation = tlz.norm(tlz.getProp('tlz._scope.vehicleDetails.myVehicle.licensePlate'));

      tlz._auto.brand = tlz.norm(tlz._sraInfos.brand);

      tlz._auto.body = tlz.norm(tlz._sraInfos.body);
      tlz._auto.gearBox = tlz.norm(tlz._sraInfos.gearBox);
      tlz._auto.version = tlz.norm(tlz._sraInfos.version);
      tlz._auto.model = tlz.norm(tlz._sraInfos.model);

<script type='text/javascript'>
  tlz.x1('ua event - download external links', function(){
    var isInternalDomain = new RegExp('(' + tlz.topDomain.replace('.', '\\.') + '|mmtro\\.com)([\\/\\?#]|$)');
    var index = tlz.contains(tlz.url, 'allsecur') ? 'empty_23' : 'title_20';
    var opt = { transport: 'beacon' };
    tlz.L2(document).on('click', 'a', function(){
      var self = this;
      var href = self.href;
      if(href){
        var trackLink = function (category, action, label){
          opt[index] = tlz.txt(self) || undefined;
          tlz.gt('event', action, tlz.merge({
            event_label: label,
            event_category: category,
            value: tlz._auto.tarif,
            transport_type: 'beacon',
            non_interaction: true
          }, opt));
        }
        var extension = href.replace('pdf.html','.pdf').match(/[\/\.](pdf|jpe?g|png|gif|(doc|ppt|xls)x?|csv|rss|zip)([\?#]|$)/i);
        if(extension){
          trackLink('download', extension[1].toLowerCase(), href);
        } else if(/^(https?:)?\/\//.test(href) && !isInternalDomain.test(href)){
          trackLink('external-link', href);
        }
      }
    });
  });
</script>

<script type="text/javascript"> 
var optionsInput = tlz.$('.quotation-option:has(.btn-primary,.btn-secondary)');
tlz._getOptionInfos = function(optionInput){
    var option = {
        title: tlz.txt(tlz.$1('h4', optionInput)).replace(/\(\d\)/, ''),
        code: optionInput.getAttribute('ng-if') && optionInput.getAttribute('ng-if').replace("haveGuaranty('", '').replace("')", '')
    };
    if(tlz._scope && tlz._scope.recommandationOptionMap && tlz._scope.recommandationOptionMap[option.code]){
        option.recommandation = tlz._scope.recommandationOptionMap[option.code].stat;
    } else {
        option.recommandation = '(not set)';
    }
    return option;
};
tlz.doForEach(optionsInput, function(optionInput){
    var optionInfos = tlz._getOptionInfos(optionInput);
  	tlz.gt('event', 'option', {
      event_label: 'affichee',
      event_category: tlz._eventCategory,
      non_interaction: true,
      option_52: optionInfos.title, 
      formuleRecommandation_53: optionInfos.recommandation
    });
});

              formuleRecommandation_53: optionInfos.recommandation

script:
<script type="text/javascript"> 
tlz.x1('privacy',function(){
  tlz._optinBanner = 'cookies'; //rule privacy
  window.tc_privacy_cookie_name = 'TC_OPTOUT_cookies';
  tlz._optin = function(type,soft) {
      if (type == 'cookies') {
          tlz.setMacro(type + 'Optin', { value: !0, user: 'als' });
          tlz.evt.send(type + 'Optin');
      }
      tlz._optinCategories = '';
      tlz.doForEach(tlz._als, function(v, k) {
          if (tlz.contains(k, 'Optin') && k != 'rgpdOptin') {
              k = k.replace('Optin', '');
              tlz._optinCategories = tlz._optinCategories ? tlz._optinCategories + ',' + k : k;
          }
      });
      tlz.ua('als.send', 'event', 'optin - cookies', 'optin',(soft || 'hard'), { dimension103: (tlz._optinCategories || 'none') });
  };
  tlz._softOptin = function() {
    tlz.x1('softoptin',function(){
      tlz._optin('cookies','soft');
      tC.privacy.In(0, tC.privacyVersion, 'ALL');
      var x = tlz.$1('#tc_privacy');
      if (x) {
          x.style.display = 'none';
          document.body.removeChild(x);
      }
    });
  };
  window.tc_showPrivacy = function() {
      if (!tlz._als.cookiesOptin) {
          tlz.trackScroll({ footerNode: tlz.$1('.region-footer') });
          tlz.evt.on('scrollDepth', function(e) {
              if (e.detail.depht == '50%' && e.detail.ratio>1.5) {
                  tlz._softOptin();
              }
          });
          tlz.L2(document).on('mouseup', '*', function() {
              if (!tlz.closest(this, '#tc_privacy,#footer_tc_privacy')) {
                  tlz._softOptin();
              }
          });
          if (tlz.random(10) === 1) { tlz.ua('als.send', 'event', 'optin - cookies', 'show banner', 'cookies', { nonInteraction: true }); }
      }
  };
  window.tc_closePrivacyCross = function() { tlz._optin('cookies'); };
});
</script>

<script type='text/javascript'>
tlz.x1('ua event - download external links', function(){
	var isInternalDomain = new RegExp('(' + tlz.topDomain.replace('.', '\\.') + '|mmtro\\.com)([\\/\\?#]|$)');
	var index = tlz.contains(tlz.url, 'allsecur') ? 'empty_23' : 'title_20';
	var opt = { transport: 'beacon' };
	tlz.L2(document).on('click', 'a', function(){
		var self = this;
		var href = self.href;
		if(href){
			var trackLink = function (category, action, label){
				opt[index] = tlz.txt(self) || undefined;
                tlz.gt('event', action, tlz.merge({
                  event_label: label,
                  event_category: category
                }, opt));
			}
			var extension = href.replace('pdf.html','.pdf').match(/[\/\.](pdf|jpe?g|png|gif|(doc|ppt|xls)x?|csv|rss|zip)([\?#]|$)/i);
			if(extension){
				trackLink('download', extension[1].toLowerCase(), href);
			} else if(/^(https?:)?\/\//.test(href) && !isInternalDomain.test(href)){
				trackLink('external-link', href);
			}
		}
	});
});
</script>

<script type='text/javascript'> 
tlz.x1('event - file error',function(){
  tlz.L2(document).on('change',':file',function(){
      var filePicker = this;
      if(filePicker.value){
          setTimeout(function(){
              var filePickerId = filePicker.getAttribute('id').replace('document','');
              var errorNodes = tlz.$('.columns-errors p[ng-show*="'+filePickerId+'"]:not(.ng-hide)');
              var errors = [];
              for (var i = 0; i < errorNodes.length; i++) {
                  errors.push(tlz.txt(errorNodes[i]));
              }
              errors = errors.join(',');
              if(errors){
                  var fileType = filePicker.value.match(/\.([^\.]+)$/) && filePicker.value.match(/\.([^\.]+)$/)[1].toLowerCase() || 'sans type';
                  errors = /format/.test(errors) && 'type incorrect : ' + fileType || /taille/.test(errors) && 'taille > 3mo';
                  tlz.gt('event', 'erreur justificatif', {
                    event_category: tlz._eventCategory,
                    event_label: filePickerId.toLowerCase() + ' - ' + errors
                  });
              }
          }, 1000);
      }
  });
});
</script>

    window._uxa.push(['setPath', tlz._customPathDevis]); // path  
    // cutom var (20 max) => Ã  dÃ©finir avec le init
    tlz._espace = tlz.path.match(/^(\/qui-est-allianz|\/recrutement)/g) ? 'marque' : (tlz.path.match(/^(\/assurances-professionnels-entreprises|\/tarif-express-pro|\/espace-client-pro\/|\/affiliation-salarie-web\/|\/arret-travail\/)/g) ? 'pro entreprises' : 'particuliers')
    tlz._pageTypeProduct = tlz._page.type + (tlz._page.product ? (' - ' + tlz._page.product) : '');
    window._uxa.push(['setCustomVariable', 1, 'univers', tlz._page.univers, 3]);

tag_name: privacy rgpd - rule, macro, trigger, ga, pc
script:
<script type="text/javascript">
tlz.x1('privacy', function() {
    // privacy center
    tlz.dR(function() {
        tlz._modifyEl = function(sel, cbk) {
            var el = tlz.$1(sel);
            if (el) { cbk(el); }
        };
        tlz._modifyEl('a[href*=utilisation-des-cookies],a[href*=gestion-des-cookies],.footer-item span:contains(cookies)', function(el) {
            el.innerHTML = ' G\xe9rer les cookies';
            el.href = '#showPrivacyCenter';
            el.setAttribute('data-destination', '#showPrivacyCenter');
        });
        tlz._modifyEl('.nx-footer .footers-cursor:contains(cookies)', function(el) { el.innerHTML = ' G\xe9rer les cookies'; });
        tlz._modifyEl('.nx-footer .nx-footer__link:contains(cookies)', function(el) { el.setAttribute('data-destination', '#showPrivacyCenter'); });
        tlz.doForEach(tlz.$('a[href="#showPrivacyCenter"],*[data-destination="#showPrivacyCenter"]'), function(link) {
            if (link.addEventListener) {
                link.addEventListener('click', function(e) { e.preventDefault();
                    e.stopPropagation();
                    window.OneTrust.ToggleInfoDisplay(); return !1; }, true);
            } else if (link.attachEvent) {
                link.attachEvent('onclick', function(e) { e.preventDefault();
                    e.stopPropagation();
                    window.OneTrust.ToggleInfoDisplay(); return !1; });
            }
        });
    });
    // set optin
    tlz._prevOptinCategories = tlz.getOptinCategories().split(',');
    tlz._saveOptin = function() {
        tlz._optinCategories = tlz.getOptinCategories();
        tlz.log('optinCategories:', tlz._optinCategories);
        tlz.gt('set', {
            optinCategories_103: tlz._optinCategories,
            hitOptinCategories_141: tlz._optinCategories
        });
        tlz.evt.send('saveOptin');
        tlz.doForEach(tlz._optinCategories.split(','), function(optinType) {
            if (!tlz.contains(tlz._prevOptinCategories, optinType)) {
                tlz.evt.send(optinType + 'Optin');
            }
        });
    };
    // cmp
    if (cmp) {
        window.cmpCallback = function(e) {
            tlz.log(e);
            tlz._banner = tlz.getProp('cmp.config.name');
            tlz.gt('set', 'bannerVersion_135', tlz.getProp('cmp.config.variant'));
            if (e.action == 'affichage') {
                tlz.gt('event', 'affichage', {
                    event_category: 'cmp - ' + tlz._banner,
                    event_label: e.from,
                    cmpShow_4: e.from == 'bandeau' ? 1 : 0,
                    non_interaction: true,
                    send_to: tlz._getConsentGaIds()
                });
            }
            if (e.action == 'sauvegarde') {
                tlz._saveOptin();
                tlz.gt('event', 'sauvegarde', {
                    event_category: 'cmp - ' + tlz._banner,
                    event_label: e.from,
                    cmpAnswer_5: e.mode != 'modification' ? 1 : 0,
                    optinAnalytics_6: tlz.isOptin('analytics') ? 1 : 0,
                    optinAds_7: tlz.isOptin('ads') ? 1 : 0,
                    non_interaction: true,
                    send_to: tlz._getConsentGaIds()
                });
            }
            if (e.action == 'retour') {
                tlz.gt('event', 'retour', {
                    event_category: 'cmp - ' + tlz._banner,
                    event_label: e.from,
                    non_interaction: true,
                    send_to: tlz._getConsentGaIds()
                });
            }
        };
        cmp.init();
    }
});
</script>

tlz._optin = function(soft) {
    if (tlz._optinType == 'rgpd') {
        if (tlz.getProp('tC.privacy.getOptinCategories')) {
            var rgpdCategories = tC.privacy.getOptinCategories();
            tlz.doForEach(rgpdCategories, function(v) {
                var subType = ({ 4: 'analytics', 10: 'analytics', 5: 'dmp', 11: 'dmp' })[v] || v;
                tlz.setMacro(subType + 'Optin', { value: !0, user: 'alz' });

            });
        }
        tlz.cookie.set('TC_OPTOUT_cookies', '0@@@001@@@ALL', { expires: 34214400 });
    }
    tlz.setMacro('cookiesOptin', { value: !0, user: 'alz' });
    tlz.evt.send('cookiesOptin');
    tlz._optinCategories = '';
    tlz.doForEach(tlz._alz, function(v, k) {
        if (tlz.contains(k, 'Optin') && k != 'rgpdOptin') {
            k = k.replace('Optin', '');
            tlz._optinCategories = tlz._optinCategories ? tlz._optinCategories + ',' + k : k;
        }
    });
    tlz.log('send', 'event', 'optin - ' + tlz._optinBanner, 'optin', tlz._optinType == 'cookies' ? (soft || 'hard') : tlz._optinCategories, { dimension103: tlz._optinCategories });

script:
<script type="text/javascript"> 
tlz.x1('privacy',function(){
  tlz._optinBanner = 'cookies'; //rule privacy
  window.tc_privacy_cookie_name = 'TC_OPTOUT_cookies';
  tlz._optin = function(type,soft) {
      if (type == 'cookies') {
          tlz.setMacro(type + 'Optin', { value: !0, user: 'als' });
          tlz.evt.send(type + 'Optin');
      }
      tlz._optinCategories = '';
      tlz.doForEach(tlz._als, function(v, k) {
          if (tlz.contains(k, 'Optin') && k != 'rgpdOptin') {
              k = k.replace('Optin', '');
              tlz._optinCategories = tlz._optinCategories ? tlz._optinCategories + ',' + k : k;
          }
      });
      tlz.ua('als.send', 'event', 'optin - cookies', 'optin',(soft || 'hard'), { dimension103: (tlz._optinCategories || 'none') });
  };
  tlz._softOptin = function() {
    tlz.x1('softoptin',function(){
      tlz._optin('cookies','soft');
      tC.privacy.In(0, tC.privacyVersion, 'ALL');
      var x = tlz.$1('#tc_privacy');
      if (x) {
          x.style.display = 'none';
          document.body.removeChild(x);
      }
    });
  };
  window.tc_showPrivacy = function() {
      if (!tlz._als.cookiesOptin) {
          tlz.trackScroll({ footerNode: tlz.$1('.region-footer') });
          tlz.evt.on('scrollDepth', function(e) {
              if (e.detail.depht == '50%' && e.detail.ratio>1.5) {
                  tlz._softOptin();
              }
          });
          tlz.L2(document).on('mouseup', '*', function() {
              if (!tlz.closest(this, '#tc_privacy,#footer_tc_privacy')) {
                  tlz._softOptin();
              }
          });
          if (tlz.random(10) === 1) { tlz.ua('als.send', 'event', 'optin - cookies', 'show banner', 'cookies', { nonInteraction: true }); }
      }
  };
  window.tc_closePrivacyCross = function() { tlz._optin('cookies'); };
});
</script>

tlz.x1('ua event - download external links', function(){
	var isInternalDomain = new RegExp('(' + tlz.topDomain.replace('.', '\\.') + '|mmtro\\.com)([\\/\\?#]|$)');
	var index = tlz.contains(tlz.url, 'allsecur') ? 'empty_23' : 'title_20';
	var opt = { transport: 'beacon' };
	tlz.L2(document).on('click', 'a', function(){
		var self = this;
		var href = self.href;
		if(href){
			var trackLink = function (category, action, label){
              	opt[index] = tlz.txt(self) || undefined;
                tlz.gt('event', action, tlz.merge({
                  event_label: label,
                  event_category: category
                }, opt));
			}
			var extension = href.replace('pdf.html','.pdf').match(/[\/\.](pdf|jpe?g|png|gif|(doc|ppt|xls)x?|csv|rss|zip)([\?#]|$)/i);
			if(extension){
				trackLink('download', extension[1].toLowerCase(), href);
			} else if(/^(https?:)?\/\//.test(href) && !isInternalDomain.test(href)){
				trackLink('external-link', href);
			}
		}
	});
});
</script>

      function init(cookieValue) {
        if (cookieValue) {
          cmk = cookieValue;

          cmk = Math.random() + "_" + Date.now();
          var tld = (function() {
            var i = 0,
                domain = document.domain,

          }

      var cookies = "; " + document.cookie;
      if (cookies) {
        var getCookie = cookies.split("; " + cn + "=");
        
        if (getCookie.length == 1) {
          init();
        } else {
          var cookieValue = getCookie[1].split(";")[0];
          init(cookieValue);
        }
      }

<script type='text/javascript'> 
  
  if(typeof s !== 'undefined'){
    
    // EVARS

      // ajouter lead by product + risk + X jours, et lead by product + risk + 30j

    // errors - pages d'erreurs

      tlz.x1('cmp show', function(){

      if (type == 'cookies') {

          tlz.evt.send(type + 'Optin');
      }
      tlz._optinCategories = '';

          }
      });
      tlz.ua('als.send', 'event', 'optin - cookies', 'optin',(soft || 'hard'), { dimension103: (tlz._optinCategories || 'none') });
  };
  tlz._softOptin = function() {

      tlz._optin('cookies','soft');
      tC.privacy.In(0, tC.privacyVersion, 'ALL');
      var x = tlz.$1('#tc_privacy');

          x.style.display = 'none';
          document.body.removeChild(x);

      if (!tlz._als.cookiesOptin) {

<script type="text/javascript"> 
  tlz.dR(function(){
    tlz.oV('functional', function(){
      if (tlz._mrh.typeHabitant == 'locataire' && (tlz._mrh.roomNb == 1 || tlz._mrh.roomNb == 2) && tlz._mrh.typeHabitation == 'appartement'){
        
        if (tlz.contains(tlz.path, 'my-tariff')){ // ta fq
          tlz.setMacro('testVariant', { session:'session', rule: function(m){ return !tlz.is(m._val) }, value: Math.floor(Math.random(2) * 3), usage:'functional' });
        }
        
        tlz.doWhen(function(){return tlz.$1('azf-side-bar .section-right:visible')}, function(){
          if (tlz._session.testVariant == 1 || tlz._session.testVariant == 2) {
            if (tlz.device() == 'desktop'){
              ((tlz.$1('azf-side-bar .section-right') || {}).style || {}).display = 'none';
            }	
          }
        });
        
        // attends l'apparition des boutons mer
        tlz.doWhen(function(){return tlz.$1('azf-button:contains(TRE APPEL):contains(PAR UN CONSEILLER):visible')}, function(){
          // 0 = version originale
          if (tlz._session.testVariant == 1) { // version sans bouton tel
            ((tlz.$1('azf-button:contains(TRE APPEL):contains(PAR UN CONSEILLER)') || {}).style || {}).display = 'none';
            ((tlz.$1('azf-button:contains(TRE APPEL):contains(PAR UN CONSEILLER) + .space') || {}).style || {}).display = 'none';
            
          } else if (tlz._session.testVariant == 2) { // version sans bouton tel et sans agent
            ((tlz.$1('azf-button:contains(TRE APPEL):contains(PAR UN CONSEILLER)') || {}).style || {}).display = 'none';
            ((tlz.$1('azf-button:contains(TRE APPEL):contains(PAR UN CONSEILLER) + .space') || {}).style || {}).display = 'none';
            ((tlz.$1('azf-button:contains(RENCONTRER):contains(UN CONSEILLER)') || {}).style || {}).display = 'none';
            ((tlz.$1('azf-button:contains(RENCONTRER):contains(UN CONSEILLER) + .space') || {}).style || {}).display = 'none';
          }
        });
           
        var testName = 'venise';
        
        if (tlz.isVal(tlz._session.testVariant)){
          tlz.setMacro('abTestInfos', { session:'session', value: testName + ' - ' + ({
              0 : 'original',
              1 : 'sans bouton tel',
              2 : 'sans bouton tel + sans agent'
            })[tlz._session.testVariant] || 'original',
          usage:'analytics' });
        }
        
        
        tlz.gt('set', {
          abTestInfos_147: tlz._session.abTestInfos
        });
      }
    });
    if (!tlz.isOptin('functional')){
      tlz.gt('set', {
          abTestInfos_147: 'venise - hors test'
      });
    }
  });
</script>

tlz.x1('listen to loaders', function(){
    tlz._loadEnd = function(state){
        if (tlz._loadStartTime){
            tlz._loadEndTime = Math.round(window.Date.now() - tlz._loadStartTime - (tlz.contains(state,'complete') ? 500 : 0));
            if (tlz._loadEndTime > 0 && tlz._loadEndTime < 300000){
                tlz.log('LOAD END', { event_category: 'mrh - loaders', name: 'from ' + tlz._loadStartState + ' to ' + state + ' on ' + (tlz._gaPath.split('?')[0]), value: tlz._loadEndTime });
                tlz._loadBasket = Math.floor(tlz._loadEndTime/1000) + ' - ' + (Math.floor(tlz._loadEndTime/1000)+1);
                tlz.gt('event', 'timing_complete '+tlz._loadBasket, { event_category: 'mrh - loaders', event_label: 'from ' + tlz._loadStartState + ' to ' + state + ' on ' + (tlz._gaPath.split('?')[0]), value: tlz._loadEndTime, transport_type: 'beacon' });
                tlz.gt('event', 'timing_complete', { event_category: 'mrh - loaders', name: 'from ' + tlz._loadStartState + ' to ' + state + ' on ' + (tlz._gaPath.split('?')[0]), value: tlz._loadEndTime, transport_type: 'beacon' });
            }
            delete tlz._loadStartState;
            delete tlz._loadStartTime;
        }
    };
    tlz.L2(document).on(['mouseup', 'click'], 'button', function(){
        if (!tlz._loadStartTime){
            tlz._loadStartState = 'click on button ' + (tlz.txt(this) || 'no_text') + ' on ' + (tlz._gaPath.split('?')[0]);
            setTimeout(function(){
                if (!tlz._loadStartTime){
                    delete tlz._loadStartState;
                }
            }, 5000);
        }
    });
    var obs = new MutationObserver(function(mutationList, observer){
        if (tlz.$1('.loader-content') && !tlz._loadStartTime){
            tlz._loadStartTime = window.Date.now();
            tlz._loadStartState = tlz._loadStartState || 'loader appeared on ' + (tlz._gaPath.split('?')[0])
            tlz.log('LOAD START', { event_category: 'mrh - loaders', event_label: 'from ' + tlz._loadStartState });
            tlz.gt('event', 'timing_start', { event_category: 'mrh - loaders', event_label: 'from ' + tlz._loadStartState, transport_type: 'beacon' });
            tlz.doWhen(function(){return !tlz.$1('.loader-content')},function(){
                            if(tlz._loadStartTime){
                                setTimeout(function(){
                                    if(tlz._loadStartTime && !tlz.$1('.loader-content')){
                                        tlz._loadEnd('complete fallback');
                                    }
                                },501);
                            }
                        },function(){
            },{interval:500, attempsToCbkKo:100, attempsToStop:100});
        } else if(tlz._loadStartTime){
            setTimeout(function(){
                if(tlz._loadStartTime && !tlz.$1('.loader-content')){
                    tlz._loadEnd('complete');
                }
            },500);
        }
    });
    obs.observe(document.querySelector('body'), { attributes: false, childList: true, subtree: true });
    window.onunload = window.onbeforeunload = (function(){
        tlz._loadEnd('exit');
    });
});
</script>

         */
    (function() {

      function callback() {
        if (!disableCallback) {

      function init(cookieValue) {

          cmk = Math.random() + "_" + Date.now();
          var tld = (function() {
            var i = 0,
                domain = document.domain,
                p = domain.split("."),

            while (i < p.length - 1 && document.cookie.indexOf(s + "=" + s) == -1) {

              document.cookie = s + "=" + s + ";domain=" + domain + ";SameSite=None;Secure";
            }
            document.cookie = s + "=;expires=Thu, 01 Jan 1970 00:00:01 GMT;domain=" + domain + ";";
            return domain;
          })();
          var now = new Date();
          var time = now.getTime();
          time += 30 * 60 * 1000;
          now.setTime(time);
          document.cookie = cn + "=" + cmk + "; expires=" + now.toUTCString() + ";path=/;domain=" + tld + ";SameSite=None;Secure";

        s.eVar164 = cmk;

      var cookies = "; " + document.cookie;
      if (cookies) {
        var getCookie = cookies.split("; " + cn + "=");
        
        if (getCookie.length == 1) {

          init(cookieValue);

    tlz.evt.on('cmp_answer',function(e){
      if(typeof s !== "undefined"){
        if(e.detail == 'modification'){ // cmp change
          s.eVar160 = tlz.getProp('cmp.config.name'); // banner version
          s.events = apl(s.events, 'event809'); // cmp change
          if(tlz.getOptinCategories() == 'none'){s.events = apl(s.events, 'event807');} // cmp refuse
          s.tl(this, 'o', 'cmp - answer ' + e.detail);
          s.clearVars();
        } else if(e.detail == 'nouveau'){ // cmp answer
          tlz.x1('cmp answer', function(){
            s.eVar160 = tlz.getProp('cmp.config.name'); // banner version
            s.events = apl(s.events, 'event811'); // cmp answers
            if(tlz.getOptinCategories() == 'none'){s.events = apl(s.events, 'event807');} // cmp refuse
            s.tl(this, 'o', 'cmp - answer ' + e.detail);
            s.clearVars();
          });
        }
      }
    });
  });
</script>

<script type="text/javascript"> 
  tlz.oV('analytics', function(){
    (function () {
      window.dataLayer = window.dataLayer || [];
      
      function gtag() {
        dataLayer.push(arguments);
      }
      gtag("js", new Date());
      
      /*
     *Name: Google Analytics CS Integration
     *Version: 1.11.0 (gtag + csMatchingKey + Inline + Tag Commander)
     */
      
      var version = "1.11.0";
      
      function callback() {
        if (!disableCallback) {
          disableCallback = true;
          
          if (window.CS_CONF) {
            window.CS_CONF.integrations = window.CS_CONF.integrations || [];
            window.CS_CONF.integrations.push("Google Analytics - v" + version);
          }
        }
      }
      
      var disableCallback = false;
      
      window._uxa = window._uxa || [];
      _uxa.push(["afterPageView", callback]);
      
      var cmk = null;
      var cn = "_cs_mk_ga";
      
      function init(cookieValue) {
        if (cookieValue) {
          cmk = cookieValue;
        } else {
          cmk = Math.random() + "_" + Date.now();
          
          var tld = (function () {
            var i = 0,
                domain = window.document.domain,
                p = domain.split("."),
                s = "_cs_tld" + new Date().getTime();
            while (i < p.length - 1 && window.document.cookie.indexOf(s + "=" + s) == -1) {
              domain = p.slice(-1 - ++i).join(".");
              window.document.cookie = s + "=" + s + ";domain=" + domain + ";SameSite=None;Secure";
            }
            window.document.cookie = s + "=;expires=Thu, 01 Jan 1970 00:00:01 GMT;domain=" + domain + ";";
            return domain;
          })();
          
          var now = new Date();
          var time = now.getTime();
          time += 30 * 60 * 1000;
          now.setTime(time);
          
          window.document.cookie = cn + "=" + cmk + "; expires=" + now.toUTCString() + ";path=/;domain=" + tld + ";SameSite=None;Secure";
        }
        
        _uxa.push([
          "trackDynamicVariable",
          {
            key: "csMatchingKey",
            value: cmk
          }
        ]);
      }
      
      var cookies = "; " + window.document.cookie;
      if (cookies) {
        var getCookie = cookies.split("; " + cn + "=");
        
        if (getCookie.length == 1) {
          init();
        } else {
          var cookieValue = getCookie[1].split(";")[0];
          init(cookieValue);
        }
      }
      
      if (cmk) {
        tlz.gt("set", {
          csMatchingKey: cmk
        });
      }
      //Google Analytics CS Integration End
      else {
        tlz.gt("config", "UA-33617477-8");
      }
    })();
  });
</script>

<script type="text/javascript">
tlz.x1('privacy', function() {
    // privacy center
    tlz.dR(function() {
        tlz._modifyEl = function(sel, cbk) {
            var el = tlz.$1(sel);
            if (el) { cbk(el); }
        };
        tlz._modifyEl('a[href*=utilisation-des-cookies],a[href*=gestion-des-cookies],.footer-item span:contains(cookies)', function(el) {
            el.innerHTML = ' G\xe9rer les cookies';
            el.href = '#showPrivacyCenter';
            el.setAttribute('data-destination', '#showPrivacyCenter');
        });
        tlz._modifyEl('.nx-footer .footers-cursor:contains(cookies)', function(el) { el.innerHTML = ' G\xe9rer les cookies'; });
        tlz._modifyEl('.nx-footer .nx-footer__link:contains(cookies)', function(el) { el.setAttribute('data-destination', '#showPrivacyCenter'); });
        tlz.doForEach(tlz.$('a[href="#showPrivacyCenter"],*[data-destination="#showPrivacyCenter"]'), function(link) {
            if (link.addEventListener) {
                link.addEventListener('click', function(e) { e.preventDefault();
                    e.stopPropagation();
                    window.OneTrust.ToggleInfoDisplay(); return !1; }, true);
            } else if (link.attachEvent) {
                link.attachEvent('onclick', function(e) { e.preventDefault();
                    e.stopPropagation();
                    window.OneTrust.ToggleInfoDisplay(); return !1; });
            }
        });
    });
    // set optin
    tlz._prevOptinCategories = tlz.getOptinCategories().split(',');
    tlz._saveOptin = function() {
        tlz._optinCategories = tlz.getOptinCategories();
        tlz.log('optinCategories:', tlz._optinCategories);
        /*tlz.gt('set', {
            optinCategories_103: tlz._optinCategories,
            hitOptinCategories_141: tlz._optinCategories
        });*/
        tlz.evt.send('saveOptin');
        tlz.doForEach(tlz._optinCategories.split(','), function(optinType) {
            if (!tlz.contains(tlz._prevOptinCategories, optinType)) {
                tlz.evt.send(optinType + 'Optin');
            }
        });
    };
    // cmp
    if (cmp) {
        window.cmpCallback = function(e) {
            tlz.log(e);
            tlz._banner = tlz.getProp('cmp.config.name');
            /*tlz.gt('set', 'bannerVersion_135', tlz.getProp('cmp.config.variant'));
            if (e.action == 'affichage') {
                tlz.gt('event', 'affichage', {
                    event_category: 'cmp - ' + tlz._banner,
                    event_label: e.from,
                    cmpShow_4: e.from == 'bandeau' ? 1 : 0,
                    non_interaction: true,
                    send_to: tlz._getConsentGaIds()
                });
            }*/
            if (e.action == 'sauvegarde') {
                tlz._saveOptin();
                /*tlz.gt('event', 'sauvegarde', {
                    event_category: 'cmp - ' + tlz._banner,
                    event_label: e.from,
                    cmpAnswer_5: e.mode != 'modification' ? 1 : 0,
                    optinAnalytics_6: tlz.isOptin('analytics') ? 1 : 0,
                    optinAds_7: tlz.isOptin('ads') ? 1 : 0,
                    non_interaction: true,
                    send_to: tlz._getConsentGaIds()
                });*/
              	tlz.evt.send('cmp_answer', e.mode);
            }
            /*if (e.action == 'retour') {
                tlz.gt('event', 'retour', {
                    event_category: 'cmp - ' + tlz._banner,
                    event_label: e.from,
                    non_interaction: true,
                    send_to: tlz._getConsentGaIds()
                });
            }*/
        };
        // auto, mrh
        if(tlz.isIframe() && tlz.getProp('cmp.config.css')){
          cmp.config.name = 'azfr partner';
          cmp.config.htmlMacros.bannerTitle = 'Ce tarificateur utilise des cookies issus de allianz.fr';
          cmp.config.css = cmp.config.css.replace('</style>','#az-cmp-banner,#az-cmp-pc{top:5% !important;transform: none;}<style>');
        }
        cmp.init();
    }
});
</script>

// Config lien CS / AA
tlz.oV('analytics', function() {
  /*
         *Name: Adobe Analytics CS Integration
         *Version: 1.9.0 (Adobe Launch + csMatchingKey)
         */
  (function() {
    var version = "1.9.0";
    function callback() {
      if (!disableCallback) {
        disableCallback = true;
        if (window.CS_CONF) {
          CS_CONF.integrations = CS_CONF.integrations || [];
          CS_CONF.integrations.push("Adobe Analytics - v" + version);
        }
      }
    }
    
    var disableCallback = false;
    window._uxa = window._uxa || [];
    _uxa.push(["afterPageView", callback]);
    var cmk = null;
    var cn = "_cs_mk_aa";
    
    function init(cookieValue) {
      if (cookieValue) {
        cmk = cookieValue;
      } else {
        cmk = Math.random() + "_" + Date.now();
        var tld = (function() {
          var i = 0,
              domain = document.domain,
              p = domain.split("."),
              s = "_cs_tld" + new Date().getTime();
          while (i < p.length - 1 && document.cookie.indexOf(s + "=" + s) == -1) {
            domain = p.slice(-1 - ++i).join(".");
            document.cookie = s + "=" + s + ";domain=" + domain + ";SameSite=None;Secure";
          }
          document.cookie = s + "=;expires=Thu, 01 Jan 1970 00:00:01 GMT;domain=" + domain + ";";
          return domain;
        })();
        var now = new Date();
        var time = now.getTime();
        time += 30 * 60 * 1000;
        now.setTime(time);
        document.cookie = cn + "=" + cmk + "; expires=" + now.toUTCString() + ";path=/;domain=" + tld + ";SameSite=None;Secure";
      }
      
      s.eVar164 = cmk;
      _uxa.push([
        "trackDynamicVariable",
        {
          key: "csMatchingKey",
          value: cmk
        }
      ]);
    }
    
    var cookies = "; " + document.cookie;
    if (cookies) {
      var getCookie = cookies.split("; " + cn + "=");
      
      if (getCookie.length == 1) {
        init();
      } else {
        var cookieValue = getCookie[1].split(";")[0];
        init(cookieValue);
      }
    }
  })();
}); // fin lien CS / AA

  if(typeof s !== 'undefined'){

  tlz.oV('analytics', function(){
    (function () {
      window.dataLayer = window.dataLayer || [];
      
      function gtag() {
        dataLayer.push(arguments);
      }
      gtag("js", new Date());
      
      /*
     *Name: Google Analytics CS Integration
     *Version: 1.11.0 (gtag + csMatchingKey + Inline + Tag Commander)
     */
      
      var version = "1.11.0";
      
      function callback() {
        if (!disableCallback) {
          disableCallback = true;
          
          if (window.CS_CONF) {
            window.CS_CONF.integrations = window.CS_CONF.integrations || [];
            window.CS_CONF.integrations.push("Google Analytics - v" + version);
          }
        }
      }
      
      var disableCallback = false;
      
      window._uxa = window._uxa || [];
      _uxa.push(["afterPageView", callback]);
      
      var cmk = null;
      var cn = "_cs_mk_ga";
      
      function init(cookieValue) {
        if (cookieValue) {
          cmk = cookieValue;
        } else {
          cmk = Math.random() + "_" + Date.now();
          
          var tld = (function () {
            var i = 0,
                domain = window.document.domain,
                p = domain.split("."),
                s = "_cs_tld" + new Date().getTime();
            while (i < p.length - 1 && window.document.cookie.indexOf(s + "=" + s) == -1) {
              domain = p.slice(-1 - ++i).join(".");
              window.document.cookie = s + "=" + s + ";domain=" + domain + ";SameSite=None;Secure";
            }
            window.document.cookie = s + "=;expires=Thu, 01 Jan 1970 00:00:01 GMT;domain=" + domain + ";";
            return domain;
          })();
          
          var now = new Date();
          var time = now.getTime();
          time += 30 * 60 * 1000;
          now.setTime(time);
          
          window.document.cookie = cn + "=" + cmk + "; expires=" + now.toUTCString() + ";path=/;domain=" + tld + ";SameSite=None;Secure";
        }
        
        _uxa.push([
          "trackDynamicVariable",
          {
            key: "csMatchingKey",
            value: cmk
          }
        ]);
      }
      
      var cookies = "; " + window.document.cookie;
      if (cookies) {
        var getCookie = cookies.split("; " + cn + "=");
        
        if (getCookie.length == 1) {
          init();
        } else {
          var cookieValue = getCookie[1].split(";")[0];
          init(cookieValue);
        }
      }
      
      if (cmk) {
        tlz.gt("set", {
          custom_map: {
            dimension146: "csMatchingKey"
          }
        });
        
        tlz.gt("config", "UA-33617477-8", {
          csMatchingKey: cmk
        });
      }
      //Google Analytics CS Integration End
      else {
        tlz.gt("config", "UA-33617477-8");
      }
    })();
  });
</script>

	var isInternalDomain = new RegExp('(' + tlz.topDomain.replace('.', '\\.') + '|mmtro\\.com|allianz\\.fr)([\\/\\?#]|$)');
	var getExtension = function(txt){
		return txt && txt.replace('pdf.html','.pdf').match(/[\/\.](pdf|jpe?g|png|gif|(doc|ppt|xls)x?|csv|rss|zip)([\?#]|$)/i);
	};
	var trackLink = function (text, category, action, label){
		tlz.gt('event', action, {
			event_label : label,
			event_category : category,
			linkTitle : text || undefined,
			transport_type : 'beacon'
		});
	};
	tlz.L2(document).on('click', 'a', function(){
		var href = this.href;
		if(href){
			var extension = getExtension(href) || getExtension(this.title);
			if(extension){
				trackLink(tlz.txt(this), 'download', extension[1].toLowerCase(), href);
			} else if(/^(https?:)?\/\//.test(href) && !isInternalDomain.test(href)){
				trackLink(tlz.txt(this), 'external-link', href);
			}
		}
	});
});
</script>

script:
<script type="text/javascript">
tlz.x1('privacy', function() {
  tlz._banner = 'ot-rgpd-default';
  if (tlz.userAgent.indexOf('MSIE ') > -1 || /trident.*rv\:11\./i.test(tlz.userAgent)) {
    tlz._banner = 'ot-rgpd-default-ie';
  }
  tlz._getBannerVariant = function(banner) {
    var bannerVariants = {
      'ot-rgpd-default': [
        // { name: 'footer avec bouton refuser', country: 'EU|MT|', weight: 10 }, // Malte
        // { name: 'popin avec bouton refuser', country: 'AS|MV|', weight: 10 }, // Maldives 
        { name: 'popin continuer sans accepter', country: 'EU|MC|', weight: 10 } // Monaco
      ],
      'ot-rgpd-partner': [{ name: 'popin continuer sans accepter', country: 'SA|GD|', weight: 10 }], // Grenade
      'ot-rgpd-outremer': [{ name: 'popin continuer sans accepter', country: 'AF|KM|', weight: 10 }], // Comores
      'ot-rgpd-default-ie': [{ name: 'footer avec bouton refuser', country: 'NA|KY|', weight: 10 }] // Tuvalu
    };
    var variants = bannerVariants[banner];
    var totalWeight = 0;
    tlz.doForEach(variants, function(variant) { totalWeight += variant.weight; });
    var selectionRand = Math.floor(Math.random() * totalWeight);
    var cumulatedWeight = 0;
    var selectedVariant = variants[0];
    tlz.doForEach(variants, function(variant) {
      if (cumulatedWeight <= selectionRand && selectionRand < cumulatedWeight + variant.weight) {
        selectedVariant = variant;
      }
      cumulatedWeight += variant.weight;
    });
    return selectedVariant;
  };
  tlz._bannerVariant = tlz.debug && tlz.getParam('banner') && { country: tlz.getParam('banner') } || tlz._getBannerVariant(tlz._banner);
  window.OneTrust = {
    geolocationResponse: {
      regionCode: tlz._bannerVariant.country.split('|')[0],
      countryCode: tlz._bannerVariant.country.split('|')[1],
      stateCode: tlz._bannerVariant.country.split('|')[2]
    }
  };
  tlz.gt('set', {
    bannerVersion_135: tlz._bannerVariant.name
  });
  // display banner
  var el = document.createElement('script');
  el.type = 'text/javascript';
  el.src = 'https://cdn.cookielaw.org/scripttemplates/otSDKStub.js';
  el.async = true;
  el.setAttribute('data-document-language', 'true');
  el.setAttribute('charset', 'UTF-8');
  el.setAttribute('data-domain-script', '4d29e63a-3ed3-425b-bbb8-67ec80dffa08' + (tlz.debug ? '-test' : ''));
  (document.getElementsByTagName('head')[0] || document.getElementsByTagName('body')[0] || document.getElementsByTagName('script')[0].parentNode).insertBefore(el, null);
  //track banner
  var banner_status = 'bandeau';
  tlz.doWhen(function() { return tlz.$1('#onetrust-banner-sdk:visible, #onetrust-pc-sdk:visible') }, function() {
    tlz.gt('event', 'affichage', {
      event_category: 'cmp - ' + tlz._banner,
      event_label: banner_status,
      cmpShow_4: 1,
      non_interaction: true,
      send_to: tlz._getConsentGaIds()
    });
    tlz.L2(document).on('mouseup', '#onetrust-pc-btn-handler', function() {
      banner_status = 'privacy center';
      tlz.gt('event', 'affichage', {
        event_category: 'cmp - ' + tlz._banner,
        event_label: banner_status,
        non_interaction: true,
        send_to: tlz._getConsentGaIds()
      });
    });
    tlz.L2(document).on('mouseup', '#close-pc-btn-handler', function() {
      banner_status = 'bandeau';
      tlz.gt('event', 'retour', {
        event_category: 'cmp - ' + tlz._banner,
        non_interaction: true,
        send_to: tlz._getConsentGaIds()
      });
    });
  }, {interval:50, attempsToStop:250});
  // set optin
  tlz._prevOptinCategories = tlz.getOptinCategories().split(',');
  tlz._saveOptin = function() {
    tlz._optinCategories = tlz.getOptinCategories();
    tlz.log('optinCategories:', tlz._optinCategories);
    tlz.gt('set', {
      optinCategories_103: tlz._optinCategories,
      hitOptinCategories_141: tlz._optinCategories
    });
    tlz.evt.send('saveOptin');
    tlz.doForEach(tlz._optinCategories.split(','), function(optinType) {
      if (!tlz.contains(tlz._prevOptinCategories, optinType)) {
        tlz.evt.send(optinType + 'Optin');
      }
    });
    tlz.gt('event', 'sauvegarde', {
      event_category: 'cmp - ' + tlz._banner,
      event_label: banner_status,
      cmpAnswer_5: 1,
      optinAnalytics_6: tlz.isOptin('analytics') ? 1 : 0,
      optinAds_7: tlz.isOptin('ads') ? 1 : 0,
      cmpLastClick_142: tlz._lastClickBanner,
      non_interaction: true,
      send_to: tlz._getConsentGaIds()
    });
    tlz._lastClickBanner = !tlz.contains(tlz._lastClickBanner, 'invalide') ? tlz._lastClickBanner + ' - invalide' : tlz._lastClickBanner;
  };
  tlz._isFirstOptanonWrapperCall = true;
  tlz._lastClickBanner = 'aucun clic';
  window.OptanonWrapper = function() {
    if (tlz._isFirstOptanonWrapperCall){
      tlz._isFirstOptanonWrapperCall = false;
    } else {
      tlz._saveOptin('valider');
    }
    tlz.L2(document).on('mouseup', '#onetrust-consent-sdk button', function(){
      tlz._lastClickBanner = tlz.txt(this);
    });
  };
});
</script>

<script type="text/javascript">
tlz.x1('ua event - download external links', function(){
	var isInternalDomain = new RegExp('(' + tlz.topDomain.replace('.', '\\.') + '|mmtro\\.com)([\\/\\?#]|$)');
  	var index = tlz.contains(tlz.url, 'allsecur') ? 'empty_23' : 'title_20';
	var opt = { transport: 'beacon' };
	tlz.L2(document).on('click', 'a', function(){
		var self = this;
		var href = self.href;
		if(href){
			var trackLink = function (category, action, label){
              	opt[index] = tlz.txt(self) || undefined;
                tlz.gt('event', action, tlz.merge({
                  event_label: label,
                  event_category: category,
                  transport: 'beacon',
                  non_interaction: true
                }, opt));
			}
			var extension = href.replace('pdf.html','.pdf').match(/[\/\.](pdf|jpe?g|png|gif|(doc|ppt|xls)x?|csv|rss|zip)([\?#]|$)/i);
			if(extension){
				trackLink('download', extension[1].toLowerCase(), href);
			} else if(/^(https?:)?\/\//.test(href) && !isInternalDomain.test(href)){
				trackLink('external-link', href);
			}
		}
	});
});
</script>

// Config lien CS / AA
tlz.oV('analytics', function() {
  /*
         *Name: Adobe Analytics CS Integration
         *Version: 1.9.0 (Adobe Launch + csMatchingKey)
         */
  (function() {
    var version = "1.9.0";
    function callback() {
      if (!disableCallback) {
        disableCallback = true;
        if (window.CS_CONF) {
          CS_CONF.integrations = CS_CONF.integrations || [];
          CS_CONF.integrations.push("Adobe Analytics - v" + version);
        }
      }
    }
    
    var disableCallback = false;
    window._uxa = window._uxa || [];
    _uxa.push(["afterPageView", callback]);
    var cmk = null;
    var cn = "_cs_mk_aa";
    
    function init(cookieValue) {
      if (cookieValue) {
        cmk = cookieValue;
      } else {
        cmk = Math.random() + "_" + Date.now();
        var tld = (function() {
          var i = 0,
              domain = document.domain,
              p = domain.split("."),
              s = "_cs_tld" + new Date().getTime();
          while (i < p.length - 1 && document.cookie.indexOf(s + "=" + s) == -1) {
            domain = p.slice(-1 - ++i).join(".");
            document.cookie = s + "=" + s + ";domain=" + domain + ";SameSite=None;Secure";
          }
          document.cookie = s + "=;expires=Thu, 01 Jan 1970 00:00:01 GMT;domain=" + domain + ";";
          return domain;
        })();
        var now = new Date();
        var time = now.getTime();
        time += 30 * 60 * 1000;
        now.setTime(time);
        document.cookie = cn + "=" + cmk + "; expires=" + now.toUTCString() + ";path=/;domain=" + tld + ";SameSite=None;Secure";
      }
      
      s.eVar164 = cmk;
      _uxa.push([
        "trackDynamicVariable",
        {
          key: "csMatchingKey",
          value: cmk
        }
      ]);
    }
    
    var cookies = "; " + document.cookie;
    if (cookies) {
      var getCookie = cookies.split("; " + cn + "=");
      
      if (getCookie.length == 1) {
        init();
      } else {
        var cookieValue = getCookie[1].split(";")[0];
        init(cookieValue);
      }
    }
  })();
}); // fin lien CS / AA

<script type="text/javascript"> 
//ga optout
tlz._disableGA = function(){
    window['ga-disable-UA-33617477-8'] = !0;
    window['ga-disable-UA-33617477-20'] = !0;
    tlz._isGADisabled = !0;
    tlz.warn('GA is disabled');
};
if (tlz.cookie.get('disable-ga')){
    tlz._disableGA();
}
//debug
if (tlz.getUrlParam('fullga')){
    tlz.js('//www.google-analytics.com/analytics_debug.js');
}
//ids GA
tlz._alzGaID = 'UA-33617477-8';
tlz._alzExemptedGaID = 'UA-33617477-20';
tlz._getConsentGaIds = function(){
  return tlz.isOptin('analytics') ? [tlz._alzGaID, tlz._alzExemptedGaID] : tlz._alzExemptedGaID;
}
//consent mode
tlz._setConsentMode = function(mode){
  tlz.gt('consent', mode || 'default', {
    ad_storage: tlz.isOptin('ads') ? 'granted' : 'denied', 
    analytics_storage: 'granted'
  });
  tlz.gt('set', 'ads_data_redaction', tlz.isOptin('ads') ? false : true);
}
tlz._setConsentMode();
tlz.x1('listen saveOptin consent update', function(){
  tlz.evt.on('saveOptin', function(){ 
    tlz._setConsentMode('update');
  });
});
//init exempted
tlz.x1('init exempt - create ga tracker', function(){
  tlz.gt('config', tlz._alzExemptedGaID, {

          dimension19 : 'rawPagePath_19',

tlz.oV('analytics', function(){

          dimension74: 'clientId', //natively replaced by true clientId

          dimension8: 'userAgent_8',
          dimension66: 'env_66',
          dimension68: 'mediaType_68',
