          dimension19: 'rawPagePath_19',
          dimension126: 'eventCategory_126',
          dimension128: 'isSupervision_128',
          dimension103: 'optinCategories_103', // end dim generiques
          dimension1: 'userType_1',
          dimension4: 'logged_4',
          dimension6: 'remembered_6',
          dimension7: 'leadId_7',
          dimension20: 'linkTitle_20',
          dimension21: 'linkDestination_21',
          dimension122: 'dynatraceCookie_122',
          dimension113: 'containerInfos_113',
          dimension134: 'privacyId_134',
          dimension135: 'privacyVersion_135',
          dimension136: 'optinAds_136',
          dimension137: 'optinAnalytics_137',
          dimension138: 'optinPerso_138',
          dimension142: 'cmpLastClick_142',
          dimension146: 'csMatchingKey'
      }
  });
  tlz.oV('ads', function(){
      tlz.gt('set', { allow_google_signals: true, allow_ad_personalization_signals: true });
  });
});
tlz._setDimensions = function(name){
  //session dims
  tlz.oV('analytics',function(){
    tlz.x1('ga_session_dim_' + name, function(){
        tlz.gt('set', {
            userAgent_8: tlz.userAgent,
            env_66: tc_vars.env || '(not set)',
            sessionId_102: tlz._session.sessionId,
            sourceAN_10: tlz._session.sourceAN,
            actionCo_27: tlz._session.actionCo,
            rawReferrer_124: tlz.referrer && !tlz.contains(tlz.referrer, 'allianz.fr') && tlz.referrer || '(not set)',
            isSupervision_128: tlz._alz.email == tlz.sha256('supervision@allianz.fr') ? '1' : '0'
        });
        tlz.oV('ads', function(){
            tlz.gt('set', 'dynatraceCookie_122', tlz.store.get('dtCookie'));

  });

      logged_4: tlz._alz.logged || '0',
      remembered_6: tlz._alz.remembered || '0',

      optinPerso_138: tlz.isOptin('functional') ? '1' : '0',

      hitOptinCategories_141: tlz.getOptinCategories(),
      sondes_140: tlz.userAgent.match(/iplabel|grandma|witbe/) ? '1' : '0'
  });
}
tlz._setDimensions('exempt');
tlz.oV('analytics', function(){
  tlz._setDimensions();
  tlz.x1('send pending events',function(){
    window.setTimeout(function(){
      tlz.doForEach(tlz._pendingGtEvents, function(gtEvent){
        if (tlz.contains(gtEvent[0], 'gtag')){ gtEvent.shift(); }
        if (!!gtEvent[2] && tlz.contains(gtEvent[2]['send_to'], tlz._alzExemptedGaID)){
          gtEvent[2]['send_to'] = tlz._alzGaID;
        }
        tlz.gt.apply(this, gtEvent);
      });
    },1);
  });
})
//path iframe
if (tlz.isIframe()){
    tlz.gt('set', { page_path: '/consultation-mrh' + tlz.path + tlz.params + '#' + tlz.angularPath + tlz.params });
}
//id1000Mercis
tlz.setMacro('id1000Mercis', { user: 'alz', value: tlz.cookie.get('__troRUID') });
tlz._pageOpt = { send_to: tlz._getConsentGaIds() };
if (tlz._alz.id1000Mercis){
    tlz._pageOpt.id1000Mercis_75 = tlz._alz.id1000Mercis;
} else {
    tlz.doWhen(function(){return !!tlz.cookie.get('__troRUID') }, function(){
      tlz.setMacro('id1000Mercis', { user: 'alz', value: tlz.cookie.get('__troRUID'), usage:'analytics' });
        tlz.x1('session_id_1000mercis', function(){
            tlz.gt('event', 'send tro ruid', { event_category: 'numberly', id1000Mercis_75: tlz._alz.id1000Mercis, non_interaction: true });
        }, 'session');
    }, function(){
 tlz.warn('no cookie "__troRUID" found') }, { attempsToCbkKo: 200 });
}
//pageview
if (!tlz.isIframe()){
    tlz.x1('pageview ga', function(){
        if (!tlz._alz.clientIdGA){
            tlz._pageOpt.event_callback = function(){
                tlz.x1('ga cbk', function(){
                    tlz.doWhen(function(){return !!tlz.getProp('window.ga.getAll') && !!tlz.getProp('window.ga.getAll')[0]  }, function(){
                        tlz.setMacro('clientIdGA', { user: 'alz', value: window.ga.getAll()[0].get('clientId'), usage:['ads', 'analytics', 'functional'] });
                        tlz.evt.send('ga');
                    }, function(){tlz.warn('ga is not ready!') }, { attempsToCbkKo: 200 });
                });
            };
        }
        tlz.gt('event', 'page_view', tlz._pageOpt);
    });
}
//onga
tlz._onGa = function(cbk){
    if (tlz._alz.clientIdGA || tlz._alz.clientIdGA){
        cbk();
    } else {
        tlz.evt.on('ga', function(){
            cbk();
        });
    }
};
</script>

script:
<script type="text/javascript">
tlz.x1('ua event - download external links', function(){
	var isInternalDomain = new RegExp('(' + tlz.topDomain.replace('.', '\\.') + '|mmtro\\.com)([\\/\\?#]|$)');
  	var index = tlz.contains(tlz.url, 'allsecur') ? 'empty_23' : 'title_20';
	var opt = { transport: 'beacon' };
	tlz.L2(document).on('click', 'a', function(){
		var self = this;
		var href = self.href;
		if(href){
			var trackLink = function (category, action, label){
              	opt[index] = tlz.txt(self) || undefined;
                tlz.gt('event', action, tlz.merge({
                  event_label: label,
                  event_category: category,
                  transport: 'beacon',
                  non_interaction: true
                }, opt));
			}
			var extension = href.replace('pdf.html','.pdf').match(/[\/\.](pdf|jpe?g|png|gif|(doc|ppt|xls)x?|csv|rss|zip)([\?#]|$)/i);
			if(extension){
				trackLink('download', extension[1].toLowerCase(), href);
			} else if(/^(https?:)?\/\//.test(href) && !isInternalDomain.test(href)){
				trackLink('external-link', href);
			}
		}
	});
});
</script>

script:
<script type="text/javascript"> 
var update_page_obj = function(){
	tlz._page_obj = [];
	var parent = "";
	tlz.doForEach(tlz.$('#contractDetails button:not(#additionalTip):visible, #contractDetails a:visible'),
	    function(e){
	    	e = tlz.clone(e);
	    	if (e.nodeName == 'BUTTON' && (!e.id || !tlz.contains(e.id, 'download-btn'))){
	    		if (tlz.closest(e, '.collapse.show') && tlz.closest(e, '.collapse.show').previousElementSibling){ // si sous-accordÃ©ons
	    			var label = "";
	    			for (i = tlz._page_obj.length-1; i>=0; i--){
	    				if(tlz._page_obj[i]['type'] == 'accordeon'){
	    					label = tlz._page_obj[i]['label'] + ' - ' + tlz.txt(e);
                          	break;
	    				}
	    			}
	    			tlz._page_obj.push({'type' : 'sous-accordeon', 'label' : label, 'status' : (e.attributes['aria-expanded'] && e.attributes['aria-expanded'].value == 'true') ? 'opened' : 'closed', 'parent' : label, 'obj' : e})
	    			parent = label;
	    		}
	    		else{ // si accordÃ©on
	    			tlz._page_obj.push({'type' : 'accordeon', 'label' : tlz.txt(e), 'status' : (e.attributes['aria-expanded'] && e.attributes['aria-expanded'].value == 'true') ? 'opened' : 'closed', 'obj' : e})
	    			parent = tlz.txt(e)
	    		}
	    	}
	    	else if (e.nodeName == 'A' || (e.nodeName == 'BUTTON' && e.id && tlz.contains(e.id, 'download-btn'))){
	    		tlz._page_obj.push({'type' : 'lien', 'label' : tlz.txt(e), 'parent' : parent, 'obj' : e})
	    	}
	    }
	);
};
var update_clics_affichages = function(){
	tlz.doForEach(tlz._page_obj,
		function(e){
			if (e.type == 'accordeon' || e.type == 'sous-accordeon'){
				if (e.status == 'closed'){
					tlz.x1('affichage - ' + e.type + e.label, function(){
                      tlz.gt('event', e.type + ' - affichage', {
                        event_category: tlz._eventCategory,
                        event_label:  e.label,
                        non_interaction: true
                      });
		            });
		            tlz.x1('ecouteur clic - ' + e.type + e.label, function(){
						tlz.L2(e.obj).on('mouseup', function(){
							tlz.x1('clic - ' + e.type + e.label, function(){
                              	tlz.gt('event', e.type + ' - clic', {
                                  event_category: tlz._eventCategory,
                                  event_label:  e.label
                                });
		                	});
		            	});
		            });
				}
                else{
                  	tlz.x1('affichage - ' + e.type + e.label, function(){});
                  	tlz.x1('ecouteur clic - ' + e.type + e.label, function(){});
                }
			}
			else if (e.type == 'lien'){
				tlz.x1('affichage - ' + e.type + e.label, function(){
                  tlz.gt('event', e.type + ' - affichage', {
                    event_category: tlz._eventCategory,
                    event_label:  e.label,
                    linkTitle_20: e.parent,
                    linkDestination_21: e.obj.href
                  });
	            });
				tlz.x1('ecouteur clic - ' + e.type + e.label, function(){
					tlz.L2(e.obj).on('mouseup', function(){
						tlz.x1('clic - ' + e.type + e.label, function(){
                          	tlz.gt('event', e.type + ' - clic', {
                              event_category: tlz._eventCategory,
                              event_label:  e.label,
                              linkTitle_20: e.parent,
                              linkDestination_21: e.obj.href
                            });
	                	});
	            	});
	            });
			}
		}
	);
};
tlz.doWhen(
  function(){
 return tlz.$1('#contractSummary') && tlz.$1('#documentsHeader')}, 
  function(){
    update_page_obj();
    update_clics_affichages();
    tlz.L2(document).on('mouseup', 'button', function(e){
      setTimeout(function(){
        update_page_obj();
        update_clics_affichages();
      }, 500)
    });
}, true);
</script>

<script type='text/javascript'> 
  
  // VISITOR API
  //var consentementPerso = '';
  //var consentementMedia = '';
  
  // Demander un ECID avec le paramÃ©trage pour l'exemption
  window.s_visitor = Visitor.getInstance(tC.internalvars.adobeOrgID, {
    trackingServer: tC.internalvars.adobeTrackingServer,

  });

if(tC.internalvars.aa_switch_exemption === 'on' || tlz.isOptin('analytics')){

  adobe.optIn.approve(adobe.OptInCategories.ANALYTICS, true); 
}

if (tC.internalvars.aa_killswitch_tracking){
  //stop all tracking in case the user explicitly opted out for all tracking

}

/* Optin pour AAM et Target

   }
   if(consentementPerso){

adobe.optIn.complete();

// APPMEASUREMENT

window.s_account = tC.internalvars.RSID;
window.s=s_gi(s_account);

//s.linkExternalFilters = 'espaceclient.allianz.fr';

// tracking automatique des downloads

s.trackInlineStats = true;  // activity map (info sur le link cliquÃ© stockÃ© dans cookie adobe 's_sq')
s.currencyCode = 'EUR'; // currency

// loadedTms
tlz._loadedTms = [];
if(window._satellite && _satellite.property){
  tlz._loadedTms.push('launch;' + _satellite.property.name + ' ' + _satellite._container.environment.stage + ';' + _satellite.buildInfo.buildDate);
}
if(window.tC){

  }
}
tlz._loadedTms.join('|');

// doPlugins config (global variables)
s.usePlugins = true;
s.doPlugins = function() {

  }

  s.eVar4 = 'espace client'; //page type

  s.eVar26 = 'D=mid'; //user adobe id
  s.eVar27 = [tlz._user.type || 'prospect', tlz._user.role || 'prospect', ''].join('|'); //user type|user role 
  s.eVar43 = [tlz.host, document.title.replace(/\|/g,'-')].join('|'); //host|page title
  s.prop51 = !tlz.contains(['gerer les cookies','veuillez cliquer ici',''], tlz.txt(tlz.$1('[data-destination="#showPrivacyCenter"],a[href="#showPrivacyCenter"]'))) + '' // is translated
  s.eVar69 = (tlz._user.type == 'expert' ? [true, true, true, false, false] : [tlz.isOptin('analytics'), tlz.isOptin('functional'), tlz.isOptin('ads'), false, tlz.getOptinCategories() == 'none']).join('|'); //are performance cookies|are functional cookies|are targeting cookies|are social cookies|are none cookies
  s.eVar151 = [tlz.getParam('source'), tlz.getParam('actionCo')].join('|').replace(/^\|$/,''); //source an|actionCo

  s.eVar155 = !tlz.cookie.get('RSESSIONID') ? '-1' : (tlz.cookie.get('RSESSIONID') % 2 != 0 ? '0' : '1'); //rsessionid
  s.eVar156 = tlz.isOptin('analytics') ? 'D=mid' : ''; //user adobe id with consent

  s.eVar60 = ['mrh', 'mrh'].join('|'); //product sub name|product name

  if(s.linkType === 'e'){
    s.linkName = s.ActivityMap.link(s.linkObject) !== 0 ? s.ActivityMap.link(s.linkObject).toLowerCase() : ''; //link Name 
    s.eVar169 = s.linkURL.length > 255 ? s.linkURL.slice(0, 126) + '...' + s.linkURL.slice(s.linkURL.length-126) : s.linkURL; //link Name

 tlz.warn('no cookie "__troRUID" found') }, { attempsToCbkKo: 200 });

}

<script type="text/javascript">
tlz.x1('ua event - download external links', function(){
	var isInternalDomain = new RegExp('(' + tlz.topDomain.replace('.', '\\.') + '|mmtro\\.com)([\\/\\?#]|$)');
  	var index = tlz.contains(tlz.url, 'allsecur') ? 'empty_23' : 'title_20';
	var opt = { transport: 'beacon' };
	tlz.L2(document).on('click', 'a', function(){
		var self = this;
		var href = self.href;
		if(href){
			var trackLink = function (category, action, label){
              	opt[index] = tlz.txt(self) || undefined;
                tlz.gt('event', action, tlz.merge({
                  event_label: label,
                  event_category: category,
                  transport: 'beacon',
                  non_interaction: true
                }, opt));
			}
			var extension = href.replace('pdf.html','.pdf').match(/[\/\.](pdf|jpe?g|png|gif|(doc|ppt|xls)x?|csv|rss|zip)([\?#]|$)/i);
			if(extension){
				trackLink('download', extension[1].toLowerCase(), href);
			} else if(/^(https?:)?\/\//.test(href) && !isInternalDomain.test(href)){
				trackLink('external-link', href);
			}
		}
	});
});
</script>

[true, true, true, false, false] : [tlz.isOptin('analytics'), tlz.isOptin('functional'), tlz.isOptin('ads'), false, tlz.getOptinCategories() == 'none']).join('|'); //are performance cookies|are functional cookies|are targeting cookies|are social cookies|are none cookies
